Issues.Body:
Example Code:

```
Form formParent = new Form();
formParent.IsMdiContainer = true;
var formChild = new Form();
formChild.TopLevel = false;
var DateStart = new DateTimePicker();
DateStart.ValueChanged += (o, s) => MessageBox.Show("Success");
formChild.Controls.Add(DateStart);
formChild.Visible = true;
formChild.Parent = formParent;

Application.Run(formParent);
```

Try changing the date, there is no messagebox.

However, when exchanging the two lines
```
formChild.Visible = true;
formChild.Parent = formParent;
```
it suddenly works.
